data.name: 龙聚金源花园洋房 (Handan City, Hebei, China)
data.description:
The project is located at the intersection of Ren Min West Road (Handan Expressway) and the tourist line in Handan City, 300 meters south of the road east, with an excellent natural environment, beautiful scenery, environment, and traffic extending in all directions. The project plans to build 12 English-style houses and 5 commercial buildings with a plot ratio of 1.5. The design specifications are based on the standard of villas. The greening rate is over 45%.


Featuring with dual gas access to the home, 1:1.5 underground parking space, and super-wide building spacing of 35 meters to 88 meters. There are facing windows in the north & south to form air convection and all rooms in the house, windows for sunlight and ventilation, which can receive sunlight entering without dark spaces.

data.name: Quill Residences (bulk purchase)
data.description:
Quill Residences is a freehold serviced residence consists of 6 unit types across a total of 552 units which located to the northeast of central Kuala Lumpur, the perfect location in the heart of Kuala Lumpur's Golden Triangle.


The Quill Residences fulfils the conveniences of life converge with absolute connectivity to major highways, public transport (LRT, Monorail, bus service), education institutions, shopping malls, hospitals and access to Kuala Lumpur’s key attraction tourist areas.


Quill Residences offers a wide range of facilities and amenities, including swimming pool, gymnasium, playground, 24-hours vigilant security patrolling with round-the- clock CCTV surveillance and access control system.
data.location: 1018, Bandar Wawasan, 50300 Kuala Lumpur, Federal Territory of Kuala Lumpur

data.name: Bayu Temiang Residensi (bulk purchase)
data.description:
Bayu Temiang Residensi is a new development project in Seremban. This low-density condominium has good connectivity with a strategic location that is accessible to major highways, public transport, schools, shopping mall, and hospitals.

The condominium is surrounded by lush landscapes and a variety of facilities (Indoor & Outdoor) available such as a clubhouse, integrated playground, and swimming pool. Residents may enjoy a greener living and modern living experience at the same time.

*Low Density
*Recreation
*Gated & Guarded
*Matured Amenities
*Variety of Facilities
*Near Major Highways
data.location: Bayu Temiang Residensi@Jalan Bayu, Bandar, Taman Nee Yan, 70200 Seremban, Negeri Sembilan, Malaysia.

data.name: Impression U-Thant
data.description:
Impression U-Thant is a freehold luxury condominium completed at year 2021. It is located at Jalan U Thant, Taman U Thant, Ampang Hilir, Kuala Lumpur.

Yong Tai, KOF Holdings, RISDA to build a high-end low density condominium named Impression U-Thant strategically located at the heart of Kuala Lumpur city center.

The 108-unit residence is catered exclusively for the high society. Distinguished by a low density of nine stories. This project offers a plethora of leading-edge essentialities invented for ultra-urbanites.

The freehold units open doors to an investment in quality, while the dual-key feature allows unit conversions into esteemed investments.
data.location: 29, Jalan U Thant, Taman U Thant, 55000 Kuala Lumpur, Wilayah Persekutuan Kuala Lumpur

data.name: The Apple Melaka
data.description:
*The 39-floor FREEHOLD The Apple appeals to all walks of life. Ideally located in the heart of Melaka with the 4-STAR INTERNATIONAL HOTEL just next door. The Apple serviced apartment is one of the tallest residency building in the state. This urban oasis is only 1km from Melaka town and just 13km from the nearest exit toll. This exclusive address is located next to The Courtyard Melaka, along with many facilities and landmarks just a short distance away. 


*There are seven type of room ranging from sizes of 474 to 2,088 sqft. The Apple will also incorporate the first dual-key system SOHO in Melaka where a majority of the units come with panoramic straits and city views.
data.location: The Apple Melaka, Lorong Haji Bachee, Kampung Bukit China, Malacca
